{"tid":1646550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[純轉]《吾屬香港》一首獻美麗香港及香港民族之樂章","createTime":"2019-10-11T10:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T10:46:28.000Z","uid":321550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc07c49c932d428f80ed1d20fe3bf8ad9812f71","tid":1646550,"uid":321550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"昨者無連登ACC 純幫佢轉過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NtqKKmOHrjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNtqKKmOHrjw&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b7589832\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NtqKKmOHrjw</a><br />\n下面Quote番佢條片堆資料<br />\n<br />\n吾屬香港 (WE HONG KONG)<br />\n作曲、作詞、編曲 : 彩凰<br />\n歌詞<br />\n看  東方之珠美麗最光<br />\n看  東方之珠熾熱猛光<br />\n看  東方之珠照亮四方<br />\n看  東方之珠世代流芳 <br />\n<br />\n破  上百艱懼  迷霧中撲火<br />\n縱  盛滿風浪  全力身去擋<br />\n愛  香港         夜明小美島 <br />\n永  是我家園  同在<br />\n<br />\n從著崎嶇百萬里路<br />\n尋覓開闢世界柱光<br />\n民族堅貞締造美夢<br />\n來無分誰我建鑄香江<br />\n<br />\n無懼犧牲捍衛這地<br />\n同共舟開拓理想鄉<br />\n能齊心擊退亂世象<br />\n嚟攜手承創最美香港<br />\n<br />\n［宣言］<br />\n「吾<br />\n 僅以<br />\n 最真心作誓言<br />\n 無論予身何方<br />\n 生至死<br />\n 亦全屬我們香港」<br />\n<br />\n現階段只係以合唱團罐頭聲暫代真人唱歌<br />\n如錄唱召募成功係會推出完成度更高版本<br />\n<br />\n&darr; 錄唱召募中 詳情參考 &darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc/edit#gid=1715938190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc%2Fedit%23gid%3D1715938190&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c0c5858b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc/edit#gid=1715938190</a><br />\n<br />\n&darr; mp3下載 &darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uFywZqM8eTJB3Ongv5zQnDY2bgP0DNAx/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1uFywZqM8eTJB3Ongv5zQnDY2bgP0DNAx%2Fview&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4142e2d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uFywZqM8eTJB3Ongv5zQnDY2bgP0DNAx/view</a><br />\n<br />\n&darr; 《吾屬香港》公開資料 &darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc/edit#gid=949821876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc%2Fedit%23gid%3D949821876&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=1e1f1801\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aXugVoMdmN0tiXcstCTCXUW4GolhG8nw4HQaUwwF9rc/edit#gid=949821876</a>"},{"pid":"8328aa377212f58a338aec56720c2fed1086a4fc","tid":1646550,"uid":321550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:46:28.000Z","msg":"尋日開左去時事台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1643659/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1643659/page/1</a><br />\n不過P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見無人理 PO埋嚟時事台"}]}